title: Want to come home to Queensland? You'll need a special permit
description: The State Government is implementing strict new rules which will apply to all Queenslanders returning home from interstate.
content:
Posted 
April 09, 2020 09:59:26
The Queensland Government is implementing strict new coronavirus rules for Queenslanders returning home from interstate.
From tomorrow night, anyone returning home will need a special permit to cross back into Queensland.
